                  <h2>A Thank You Note To All The Guys Who Rejected Me</h2>
                            <hr style=" border: solid 1px #fff; margin:10px auto 10px auto;" />
             
                           
<p>This one’s for all of those who left me for the old me. Thank you for letting me transform myself into what I am today. Thank you. Thank you so much</p>
<p>Hey what do you think? That you were the cherry on my cake?</p>
<p>Oops let me tell you, though I considered you a lot but you were always fake.</p>


<p>Avoidance, rejection, ignorance were just words before you.</p>
<p>And why do I had to go through all these? I seriously don’t have any clue.</p>

<p>You were the one who left me broken,</p>
<p>Because for you I was just an ordinary token.</p>

<p>Your behavior was becoming cold,</p>
<p>I still managed and made myself bold.</p>

<p>Living happily with you was my only urge,</p>
<p>Although we were on the roads which would never merge.</p>

<p>Glad you made me realize that I wasn’t worth your time,</p>
<p>Giving all the love to you was my only crime.</p>

<p>Your good bye words were no less than a deadly pain,</p>
<p>But thank you, because I never let them go in vain.</p>

<p>Your actions made me change myself,</p>
<p>You are the prime reason for that. Don’t trust me? You Can ask yourself.</p>


<p>Thank You for letting me change my fate ,</p>
<p>There’s nothing left behind for you in me other than hate.</p>

<p>No grudge or hard feelings for you,</p>
<p>There’s just a very big thank you.</p>

<p>Now I have become more sensible and wise,</p>
<p>I Don’t care about others and their advice.</p>


<p>I’m fortunate to you for reveling all the boys real face,</p>
<p>And without you my life is moving with a better pace.</p>

<p>I am no more of an emotional fool,</p>
<p>The behavior you deserve is nothing but cruel.</p>

<p>I gave you my every little thing,</p>
<p>But for you I was nothing.</p>

<p>I badly wish to never see you again,</p>
<p>As all your memories are flushed in the drain.</p>

<p>The value I gave you was special which now you will never find.</p>
<p>Because you were the one who rejected me, just keep this in mind.</p>

<p>You were the wrong one whom I used to admire,</p>
<p>You were the only one Who left me alone in fire.</p>

<p>For all that has happened to me, thanks to you</p>
<p>You have realized a lot but my revenge is still due.</p>

<p>You were the one who let me burn,</p>
<p>Dignity is the thing which is missing so just go and learn.</p>

<p>So, this all was for you Mr. Arrogant,</p>
<p>I hope soon or later this shit would end.</p>


